❌ Using "[Number] [adjective] ideas" as the default formula for every inspiration page
❌ Ending every description with "here's how to find yours"

What GOOD looks like:
✅ The hook comes from the specific search anxiety or desire of that page's user
✅ Each title reads like it was written for one person searching for one thing
✅ Descriptions use different emotional entry points — fear, excitement, identity, frustration, curiosity — page by page
✅ Power words are used once across the session, not recycled

